{"tid":824746,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"安永: 提醒員工因公司壞升降機，預留更多時間上班","createTime":"2018-09-17T08:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T08:11:16.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"720ab71bcb536867f78e5cf8deb515631009cbb8","tid":824746,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:11:16.000Z","msg":"超強颱風山竹風襲香港後，港九各區到處滿目瘡痍，多條主要馬路、幹線佈滿被強風吹倒的大樹、垃圾等，全港交通幾近癱瘓，政府拒宣佈停工，大批打工仔直到早上10時仍塞在港鐵站未能上車。香港四大會計師行，羅兵咸、德勤以及畢馬威「3大」向員工發電郵表示，因應交通情況，可不用回公司，選擇Home office工作。至於安永，最新通知員工，因公司壞升降機，溫馨提醒員工預留時間上班。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180917/58690650\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180917%2F58690650&d=XW%2Bx1RxpNmsuaiIKIWoQWU4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=6e7bfe79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180917%2F58690650&h=fc5a4e05\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180917/58690650</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}